---
<section class="bg-transparent text-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Simple, powerful, and intuitive</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-12 text-lg">Just a few lines of code to get your API up and running.</p>

    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-xl text-left max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 border-b border-gray-700">
        <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Example.js</span>
        <button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white" title="Copy to clipboard">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-copy"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"></path></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 overflow-x-auto">
        <pre class="text-sm">
<code class="language-javascript whitespace-pre font-mono" is:raw>
